text: @FredTJoseph I am a single mom in Arizona. I lost my serving job due to covid19 and I do not qualify monetarily for unemployment. So as of right now I am waiting on the pandemic unemployment assistance, but it won’t be paid out until May 12. #RENTRELIEF $jensnazzy
